Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff was born in 1138, in Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Hugh MacDuff of Fife. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1138–":"1138–Surnud","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1165–1214":"1165–1214","1138–Female":"1138–Surnud","1138":"1138","1214":"1214","1135":"1135","1165":"1165","1195":"1195","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1138–":"1138–Kuollut","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1165–1214":"1165–1214","1138–Female":"1138–Kuollut","1138":"1138","1214":"1214","1135":"1135","1165":"1165","1195":"1195","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1138–":"1138–Décédée","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1165–1214":"1165–1214","1138–Female":"1138–Décédée","1138":"1138","1214":"1214","1135":"1135","1165":"1165","1195":"1195","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff est née en 1138, à Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Hugh MacDuff of Fife. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1138–":"1138–Verstorben","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1165–1214":"1165–1214","1138–Female":"1138–Verstorben","1138":"1138","1214":"1214","1135":"1135","1165":"1165","1195":"1195","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff wurde 1138 in Wemyss, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Hugh MacDuff of Fife mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":